snippet.title: Natsumiii & Lilypichu - Summertime Cover ♫
snippet.description:
lily and I bringing back the AYAYA ~ hope you guys enjoy this fun remake of summertime!

• ================ •

Original: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KMTo2LmixqQ
Singer: Lilypichu | https://www.youtube.com/lilypichu
Producer: Holder | https://twitter.com/MajorLeagueWobs
Video Editor: Wick | https://twitter.com/alderwicked
Art: Sae | https://twitter.com/Sae_Art // Lily | https://twitter.com/LilyPichu

• ================ •
